library('tidyverse')

Profiling in R

  • Explained on Posit Website

For example

library('profvis')
# help(package = 'profvis')
profvis({
  data(diamonds, package = "ggplot2")

  plot(price ~ carat, data = diamonds)
  m <- lm(price ~ carat, data = diamonds)
  abline(m, col = "red")
})
profvis({
  rnorm(1e5)
  rnorm(1e6)
  rnorm(1e7)
  rnorm(1e8)
})
